hudson.plugins.tfs.telemetry

Class TelemetryHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • hudson.plugins.tfs.telemetry.TelemetryHelper

  • public final class TelemetryHelper
extends Object
    The TelemetryHelper class is a singleton that allows the plugin to capture telemetry data when the user initiates events.
